title: Boise State kicker has hilarious reaction when no one would high-five him
text:
Boise State kicker has hilarious reaction when no one would high-five him FOX Sports 
Oct 5, 2015 at 2:42p ET + Updated Oct 5, 2015 at 2:44p ET 
Rejection stings. Everybody knows that. But it can especially hurt right after you've successfully completed a task, and it's like nobody even cares. 
Boise State kicker Tyler Rausa knows the feeling all too well. After drilling a field goal against Hawaii on Saturday, Rausa just wanted a little love from his teammates. And they completely ignored him. 
So how did Rausa respond? Like any true entertainer would -- he celebrated all by himself. And it was a much better celebration than any high-five would have been. â€” Will Hall (@WillHallKTVB) October 4, 2015 
Don't let the haters knock you down, Tyler. Just keep being yourself.
